e_5(50!)=\sum_{i\geq 1}\left\lfloor \dfrac{50}{5^{i}}\right\rfloor=\left\lfloor \dfrac{50}{5}\right\rfloor +\left\lfloor \dfrac{50}{5^{2}}\right\rfloor =10+2=12.
